    "description": "Are you a skilled Sales Manager looking for your next big career move? Savills India in Noida offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Savills India:\nSavills India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Savills India!",
